:01:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"313d962b22878a94bcc296105dffcb67a2879138","tid":1890540,"uid":267915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"63c7050f2697d0f1b267924178771c5d5044ff30","tid":1890540,"uid":163492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2a4626e31bcac0fe2b4aa71e03d085c6ea8775a2","tid":1890540,"uid":267915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T08:58:40.000Z","msg":"話說工人姐姐係我屋企做左四年，期間一直都好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老母係啲典型閪老細黎，係要卒人卒到最勁先罷休<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n例如，我老母係個所有野都要絕對乾淨既人黎，以前未係呢個工人姐姐既時侯，有鋪癮係要等我地成家訓哂（包括我當時既工人姐姐）之後拎哂所有工人姐姐洗過既碗碟出黎再洗一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。我地成家人勸左佢一排，唔想佢日日咁夜訓做埋啲咁既野，老母應承左唔凌晨洗碗，但每日食飯前要好似係酒樓咁用熱水過一次所有碗碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。咁都算啦，但自從呢個工人姐姐黎左之後，我老母癲到每晚食飯個時都要<strong>拎哂成個碗櫃啲碗碟出黎</strong>（包括當晚開飯唔需要用到晚碗碟），逐個碟用餸汁整污糟佢so that我工人姐姐會洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n又例如，我老母要求成屋都一塵不染，但佢只會容許<strong>主人房個廁所</strong>係痴左線咁凌亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地個廁所角落有一個垃圾桶，我老母會特登用一堆濕哂既紙巾團掉落個個角落（就係特登唔瞄準個垃圾桶口），務求增加工人姐姐執廁所既workload<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />簡單啲講，我屋企個廁所核突程度係衰過啲商場廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n以上只係其中一兩個例子。各位巴絲唔洗勸我勸服我老母唔好咁痴線，有興趣就起我底去睇我之前開過既po<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，就會明我老母呢個格冇得救。<br />\n<br />\n簡單啲講，我剩係想表達，我真係好鄧工人姐姐開心，終於擺脫呢個人工俾得又少又閪既老細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。希望下一個家庭對你好啲，同埋真係好對唔住咁多年黎都唔係好幫到你解圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\nbtw請善用不摧文回覆。今日721 七個月喇，大家集中推721 po上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:14:27.000Z","msg":"我老母都係咁 冇咁嚴重<br />\n佢勁鍾意執屋<br />\n成日執到我D野 唔見曬<br />\n<br />\n覺得佢有問題係<br />\n因為去旅行 晚晚都係房執 <br />\n一兩個鐘頭野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T10:04:11.000Z","msg":"去旅行都執兩個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />伯母實在太有心力"},{"pid":"156a2b512cec0e9c614f4c7a13b0285a920430bf","tid":1890540,"uid":26773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:24:16.000Z","msg":"咁唔洗請啦 自己做埋咪得"},{"pid":"78d0e18326645b7ff1c8f5754224b1edd6d7a610","tid":1890540,"uid":309664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:27:28.000Z","msg":"工人姐姐好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁工人有無俾面色你呀媽睇"},{"pid":"58bddeadcc7fd575b3075579172dbe398115b55e","tid":1890540,"uid":313426,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:35:28.000Z","msg":"老母有病<br />\n西女人嚟<br />\n唔好請工人慳番啲錢"},{"pid":"9276d02ba8bb7c35e133d5ba439ff482db57c4aa","tid":1890540,"uid":229834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfcfcc20feb289e1f2c1a434801a28d3655a3671","tid":1890540,"uid":92401,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"感情台?<br />\n<br />\n咁感人你扑左個工人未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:39:37.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n<br />\n原來你感情得扑野<br />\n<br />\n想知你對你親生老母有冇感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93e5d4fb50d8d7526285b8978710e50b90334be","tid":1890540,"uid":254410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:41:39.000Z","msg":"咁工人姐姐默默硬食無反抗?"},{"pid":"c467e6b3987de362ce8d700e7c235cb38d4894f0","tid":1890540,"uid":92401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9276d02ba8bb7c35e133d5ba439ff482db57c4aa","tid":1890540,"uid":229834,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfcfcc20feb289e1f2c1a434801a28d3655a3671","tid":1890540,"uid":92401,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T09:08:13.000Z","msg":"感情台?<br />\n<br />\n咁感人你扑左個工人未"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T20:39:37.000Z","msg":"好慘<br />\n<br />\n原來你感情得扑野<br />\n<br />\n想知你對你親生老母有冇感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T07:12:42.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"671d369dfb2db976b7da0f8529cec937cb6437e7","tid":1890540,"uid":257320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T14:34:41.000Z","msg":"下個工人咪慘囉"}]}